OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with largely clear skies and
OL,7,Fevening sunshine to start but turning
OL,8,Fcloudier. Dry and mostly cloudy
OL,9,Fovernight with clear intervals in the
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,13,Fvariable cloud but still plenty of
OL,14,Flong sunny spells. Feeling warm in the
OL,15,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
